summary: A STONE FROM A WEED-EATER HIT MY WINDSHIELD AS I WAS DRIVING (~25 MPH) AND WITHIN 5 MILES THE CRACK WAS ALREADY 18 INCHES.  IN SEARCHING ONLINE I NOTICED A LOT OF OWNERS MENTIONED WINDSHIELD PROBLEMS AND HOW THIN THE WINDSHIELD IS.  I WOULD HAVE EXPECTED A SLIGHT CHIP BUT NOT THE CRACK.  THE TEMPERATURE WAS MID 70'S.
